<h2>Blue colored skin and Visible bugs or parasites</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms blue colored skin and visible bugs or parasites including Lice, Tetralogy of Fallot, and Cold exposure.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with blue colored skin and visible bugs or parasites. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
